snippet.title: Hot Wheels Stunt Track Driver: Intro
snippet.description: So yeah, after watching some playthroughs, I pulled out my copy of this game and reinstalled it. Initially I was going to do a tournament run with this as the start, but, I fucked up the recording beyond repair somehow (recorded it wrong) and that didn't happen. Here is the intro in its own video. Looks OK for 1998, actually.
